electron2pdf SlackBuild (repackaging)

This SlackBuild repackages the prebuilt Linux tarball produced in ../dist/
into a Slackware package that installs to /opt/electron2pdf/.

Build:
  cd slackware
  chmod +x electron2pdf.SlackBuild
  ./electron2pdf.SlackBuild

Install:
  installpkg /tmp/electron2pdf-*.tgz

After installation:
  /usr/bin/electron2pdf will run /opt/electron2pdf/bin/electron2pdf
